headline: West Pharmaceutical Services to Present at the CJS 25th Annual "New Ideas for the New Year" Investor Conference
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), a global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that Cindy Reiss-Clark, Sr. VP and Chief Commercial Officer; Chad Winters, VP of Finance and Chief Accounting Officer; and John Sweeney, VP of Investor Relations, will present at the CJS 25th Annual "New Ideas for the New Year" Virtual Investor Conference on January 14, 2025 at 10:15 a.m. ET.
